OL,10,GEthics: a necessary reign or a
OL,11,Ghindrance to scientific progress? An
OL,12,Gapocryphal story describes how if one
OL,13,Gdrops a frog into boiling water, it
OL,14,Gwill jump out. However, if the frog is
OL,15,Gdropped into warm water which is then
OL,16,Gslowly heated, it will boil to death.
OL,17,GIn science, leaving the lukewarm water
OL,18,Gmeans abandoning research that could
OL,19,Glead to groundbreaking discoveries --
OL,20,Gbut when is the water too hot? How do
